flowchart TD
    A[读取 issue.md] --> B[扫描目标仓库<br/>collect_repo_context]
    B --> C[LLM Step 1: 生成计划<br/>PlanDraftModel]
    C --> D[LLM Step 2: 生成代码编辑<br/>EditPlanModel]
    D --> E{approve-write?}

    E -->|No| F[blocked-awaiting-approval]
    E -->|dry-run| G[dry-run-proposed]
    E -->|Yes| H[backup_repo_files<br/>快照原始文件]

    H --> I[apply_write_action<br/>exact string replace]
    I --> J[run_validation<br/>make test in target repo]
    J --> K{test passed?}

    K -->|Yes| L[persist_run_artifacts]
    K -->|No| M{retry < 2?}

    M -->|No| L
    M -->|Yes| N[rollback_repo_files<br/>恢复原始文件]
    N --> O[LLM Retry: 带 test output<br/>重新生成 edit proposals]
    O --> P[prepare_write_action<br/>更新 payload]
    P --> H

    L --> Q[输出 artifacts]
    Q --> R[plan.json]
    Q --> S[patch.diff]
    Q --> T[pr_draft.md]
    Q --> U[test_report.json]

    subgraph Providers
        direction LR
        P1[deterministic]
        P2[gemini-cli]
        P3[claude-code-cli]
        P4[codex-cli]
    end

    C -.-> Providers
    D -.-> Providers
    O -.-> Providers

    subgraph RepoScan[repo scan]
        B1[list_files]
        B2[read_file]
        B3[code_search]
    end

    B -.-> RepoScan
